for (int i = 0; i < 256; i++) {
  Esplora.writeRGB(0, i, i);
  delay(20);
}
```
Finally to make it blue, we add another `for` loop.
```norun;
for (int i = 0; i < 256; i++) {
  Esplora.writeRGB(0, 0, i);
  delay(20);
}
```
